<lb ed="L" n="0482b15"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="1"><cb:jhead>龍池幻有禪師語錄卷之一</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb ed="L" xml:id="L153.1637.0483a" n="0483a"/>
<lb ed="L" n="0483a01"/><cb:div type="w"><head>音釋</head>
<lb ed="L" n="0483a02"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form>瘥</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0483a0202" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">楚懈切音衩疾愈也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB15080">󳫨</g></term></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0483a0211" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">蒲巴切音琶搔也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>椰</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0483a0219" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">余<term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB17327">󴎯</g></term>切音邪作枒椰子木
<lb ed="L" n="0483a03"/>名出交州其葉背面相似</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>痰</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0483a0312" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">徒監切音談病液</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>醯</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0483a0320" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">奚夷切音橀酸也酢末也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="L" n="0483a04"/><entry><form>賄</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0483a0402" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">虎猥切音悔財也財帛總名</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
